{"title":"朝鲜谚语","authors":["昌熙"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊患难之交，永远忘不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊有志者能使石头长出草来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊一只蛤蟆能弄浊整塘清水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊三个盲人凑在一起能看一封信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊猎手家的小狗不怕虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊狼嚎叫，狗翘尾巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊在所有痛苦中，亡国之苦最难忍受。〔昌熙辑译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}